page.title: 20ST.LAURENCE'S CHURCH/CREDITS
page.content: St.Laurence's Church dates from 1120 though the chancel is Saxon and the tower Victorian.In the 13th century with the increase in size of the village an aisle was added to the northern side of the church.The church which contains Norman and Gothic arches,is in need of repair.
